---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Open Climate Resilience Policies">
  <h1>Open Climate Resilience Policies</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    OCRP is an open source library of model policies designed to reduce climate-related losses for governments at all levels.
  </p>
  
  <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
    <h2>About the Project</h2>
    <p>
      Climate change poses unprecedented challenges to communities worldwide. The Open Climate Resilience Policies project 
      provides government officials, policymakers, and community leaders with tested, adaptable policy frameworks to 
      address climate hazards and build resilience.
    </p>
  </section>
  
  <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Each policy in the OCRP library includes:
    </p>
    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Clear implementation guidelines</li>
      <li>Applicability to different government levels</li>
      <li>Fiscal impact assessments</li>
      <li>Evidence-based best practices</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <p>
      Explore our <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}policies/`}>policy library</a> to find resilience solutions 
      tailored to your community's needs.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
